{"tid":2092002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"憂留「罪證」網民紛撤文退群組  周保松不刪帖：拒活於恐懼","createTime":"2020-07-03T03:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T03:51:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"19715a8a726df1277cab1990eb8a5ae46b293d5d","tid":2092002,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:50:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/TE3WYNV47DUGOCE26JHORDMTGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FTE3WYNV47DUGOCE26JHORDMTGI%2F&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=c996c120\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FTE3WYNV47DUGOCE26JHORDMTGI%2F&h=dbbfaf3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/TE3WYNV47DUGOCE26JHORDMTGI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n憂留「罪證」網民紛撤文退群組 <br />\n周保松不刪帖：拒活於恐懼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zB1JUMl2wjSvZXM03SRpHjrMC_I=/539x410/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3Y2ZNINGH7ZKMEUQU7NSWVSW3U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzB1JUMl2wjSvZXM03SRpHjrMC_I%3D%2F539x410%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3Y2ZNINGH7ZKMEUQU7NSWVSW3U.gif&h=0aa3b581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中大政治與行政學系副教授周保松昨表明，不會改名、不會刪去過去文字和相片。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【兩制蓋棺】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法生效，惟涵蓋範圍極闊兼定義含糊，最高更可判終身監禁。學者形容本港瀰漫白色恐怖，不少人近日紛紛刪除社交媒體賬號和帖文，甚至退出群組。有大律師認為，若有關帖文在法例生效前張貼，不應視為條例適用，因條例沒列明有追溯力。不過，中大政治與行政學系副教授周保松和黃之鋒均表明，不想因過度擔心而活在恐懼當中，因此不會改名、不會刪去文字和相片。<br />\n<br />\n藝人王喜因主持<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒轉載：說中我想法<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：傳媒隨時中招 譚耀宗：明眼人識分<br />\n<br />\n不過，港版國安法實施首天，周保松在其fb專頁發文，表明不會改名、不會刪去過去文字和相片，亦不會放棄自己的觀點和立場，「我不想被人審查，更不想自我審查」。他不想過度擔心，以至令自己無時無刻活在恐懼當中，「因為恐懼一旦入侵人心，我們就很難活成自己想要的樣子」。該帖文獲近5,000個讚好和逾620次轉載分享。黃之鋒昨日亦在其fb專頁轉載周保松的帖文，最後加上hashtag（標籤）「感謝周保松教授說中我的想法」。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究中心的總監鍾劍華表示，港版國安法有66條法律條文，內容空泛且界線模糊<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n「冇預計有呢啲（退出群組）情況，但就正正係中共想達到嘅目的」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TJ8vSh24gnPEWKMcD3ZLVBxq9WE=/411x441/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QB7GEHFMVSJNRIR7DHWDPX72QU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTJ8vSh24gnPEWKMcD3ZLVBxq9WE%3D%2F411x441%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQB7GEHFMVSJNRIR7DHWDPX72QU.gif&h=a5728ae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前日市民在銅鑼灣被警員截查搜袋，市民擔心其私隱被侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大律師：減低犯法風險<br />\n<br />\n大律師黃宇逸認為，「風險幾時都會有，但delete（刪除賬戶、發文）會減低（觸犯國安法）風險」，但若有關帖文在法例生效前張貼，不應視為條例適用，因條例沒列明有追溯力。"},{"pid":"03dbf1692c6a0592e18114da4ff186ac23c9e443","tid":2092002,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:51:16.000Z","msg":"周教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}